list.abstract: level，英文单词，可作名词、形容词和动词，翻译为水平、标准、水平面、平坦的、瞄准、使同等等意思。
《LEVEL》是韩国乐队组合神话演唱的一首歌曲，由김이나作词，김도현、김주현作曲，收录于神话2018年8月28日发行的专辑《SHINHWA TWENTY SPECIAL ALBUM ‘HEART’》中。

yingyinNormal.en: I got a real problem here. I could raise my level. But I know if I do, it'll only make her raise her level, too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在真的碰上大麻烦了，我可以提高我的水平，但我知道如果我这样做，只会刺激她也提高她的水平。

yingyinNormal.en: What are you gonna do about Spanish class? I'm going to have to raise my level, too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 西语课你打算怎么办？我也打算提高我的水平。

yingyinNormal.en: Bricks must be laid straight on level, see? Line after line. That will take ages. Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 必须要把砖块沿水平的直线砌好，看？一层一层地砌。这样的话要花很长时间！是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Bricks must be laid straight on level, see? Line after line. That will take ages. Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 必须要把砖块沿水平的直线砌好，看？一层一层地砌。这样的话要花很长时间！是的。

yingyinNormal.en: It has to matter that who we were affects who we are. You chose Smackle because you want to raise your level. That's who you are.
yingyinNormal.zh: 过去的我们对现在的我们也有很重要的影响，你选择了史麦科是因为你想提高你的水平，这就是你啊。

yingyinNormal.en: For years, they've been running jobs in Europe, but it's their most recent jobs that graduated them to a whole new level. Three targets, highly specific.
yingyinNormal.zh: 近年来，他们一直在欧洲活动，这些是他们最近干的几票，水平大有提高，三个目标非常明确。

yingyinNormal.en: No. He's too low level. He knew nothing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有，他级别太低，什么都不知道。

yingyinNormal.en: See, Han? The world's different above sea-level.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看吧，阿憨？海平面上的世界大不同啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Level three, and she thinks she's rich. What a newb.
yingyinNormal.zh: 才3级就觉得自己发财了，真是个新手。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, we always anticipate a certain level of graft.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们早预计会遇到一定程度的腐败。

yingyinNormal.en: A certain level? He's egregious. The man's a monster.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一定程度？他是个贪婪透顶的恶魔。

yingyinNormal.en: They were identified as low level Chechen separatist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 经确认他们的身份为普通车臣独立武装分子。

yingyinNormal.en: Five shillings an hour. Maybe a little more for A-level.
yingyinNormal.zh: 1小时5先令，可能高级考试会多些。

yingyinNormal.en: What's going on? Leonard, guess what? I'm a level-three warrior.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么回事？莱纳德，我是一个3级战士了。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a week, the first level down. Six months the second level down, and the third level...
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一层约一星期，第二层约六个月 至于第三层。。。

yingyinNormal.en: What level is that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 是什么级别?

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe on some level.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能有一点。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I'm not a master, but let's just start at zero. Level zero. No. There is no such thing as level zero.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不是大师，但是我们能从零开始吗?零级。 不，这没有东西是零级的。

yingyinNormal.en: And this is optional. This is if you want to take it to the next level and I'm gonna take it to the next level.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过这个看个人选择，如果你想到更高一级别的话，我就带你到更高一级别。

yingyinNormal.en: No. Best thing is not to comment. It lowers us to their level.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，最好的处理方法就是不作评论，否则我们会沦为跟他们同一档次。

examination_example.sentence: A balanced breakfast is really helpful, but getting regular meals throughout the day is more important to leave blood sugar stable through the day, which helps control weight and hunger <highlight>levels</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 均衡的早餐真的很有帮助，但一整天的规律饮食，对保持全天血糖稳定更重要，而且有助于控制体重和饥饿水平。

examination_example.sentence: After four months, the patients using the computerized CBT programs had no improvement in depression <highlight>levels</highlight> over the patients who were only getting usual care from their doctors.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 四个月后，与只接受常规治疗的患者相比，接受线上认知行为疗法的患者的抑郁水平并没有得到改善。

examination_example.sentence: Rather than saying, ‘ This is science, over here is history, 'I see schools taking this idea of projects and looking at: How do they support children in higher <highlight>level</highlight> learning?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我想象学校将不再说“这是科学，这是历史”，而是采纳“项目”这一概念并思考一个问题：如何帮助孩子进行更高层次的学习？

examination_example.sentence: Around 9 in 10 people in low- and middle- income countries live in places where they regularly experience dangerous <highlight>levels</highlight> of outdoor air pollution. But the problem is not limited exclusively to the developing world.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在低收入和中等收入国家，大约十分之九的人生活在他们经常经历户外空气污染处于危险程度的地方。但这个问题并不仅限于发展中国家。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Levels</highlight> of outdoor pollution have grown rapidly along with rapid growth in industry and transportation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 随着工业和交通的快速增长，室外污染水平迅速上升。

examination_example.sentence: Those shifts have yet to be reflected in record obesity <highlight>levels</highlight>, which stand at 36.5% overall in the US.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些转变尚未反映在创纪录的肥胖水平中，美国的肥胖率大体上为36.5%。

examination_example.sentence: The trouble with those things is that within six months to a year, people are back to their original baseline <highlight>levels</highlight> of well-being.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 问题是，在6个月到1年的时间里，人们又回到了最初的幸福基线水平。

examination_example.sentence: Things are not as bad as they once were but, according to the American Lung Association, Los Angeles is still the worst city in the United States for <highlight>levels</highlight> of pollutants.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然情况没有以前那么糟糕，但根据美国肺脏协会(American Lung Association)的数据，洛杉矶仍然是美国污染物水平最差的城市。

examination_example.sentence: At the primary <highlight>level</highlight>, the main aim is to cultivate good habits, like learning to plan and exercising self-discipline.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在初级阶段，主要目的是培养好习惯，比如学习计划和锻炼自律。

examination_example.sentence: At senior <highlight>levels</highlight>, only a quarter of professors are women.

examination_example.sentence: "Climate change" more broadly referred to the numerous effects of this increase, such as sea-<highlight>level</highlight> rise and ocean acidification (酸化) .
examination_example.sentence_trans: “气候变化”更广泛地指的是这一增长的众多影响，如海平面上升和海洋酸化。

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a position on a real or imaginary scale of amount, quantity, extent, or quality
sense_info_list.zh: 等级; 水平; 水准; 程度

examination_example.sentence: Many learning apps provide rich courses for the learners to meet their <highlight>levels</highlight> of knowledge and interests.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多学习软件为学习者提供丰富的课程，以满足他们的知识水平和兴趣。

examination_example.sentence: The robot can judge the skill <highlight>levels</highlight> of human players exactly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 机器人可以准确判断人类选手的技术水平。

examination_example.sentence: Higher <highlight>levels</highlight> of physical activity (more than 90 minutes per day) can reduce the risk of diabetes by 28 %.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 更高水平的体育活动(每天运动90分钟以上)可以降低28 %的糖尿病风险。

sense_info_list.en: a height or distance from the ground or another stated or understood base

examination_example.sentence: Sea <highlight>levels</highlight> will rise and many cities along the sea will disappear.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 海平面将上升，许多沿海城市将消失。

examination_example.sentence: It is the highest railway in the world, climbing 5,000 meters above sea <highlight>level</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它是世界上最高的铁路，爬升到海拔5000米。

examination_example.sentence: The father said his younger child was still on the upper <highlight>level</highlight> of the house but he didn't know where.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这位父亲说，他的小儿子还在房子的上层，但他不知道在哪里。

sense_info_list.en: a horizontal plane or line with respect to the distance above or below a given point

examination_example.sentence: Built on platforms (平台), they will rise with the sea <highlight>level</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它们建在平台上，会随着海平面上升。

examination_example.sentence: Qomolangma, the world Highest mountain is about 8, 848 metres above sea <highlight>level</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 珠穆朗玛峰是世界上最高的山峰，海拔约8848米。

examination_example.sentence: The floating cities could move up with the sea <highlight>level</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 漂浮的城市会随着海平面上升。
